---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="skills stack gap-4">
	<header>
		<h2>Documentation strengths</h2>
	</header>
	<div class="skill-grid">
		<div class="skill-card">
			<div class="skill-header">
				<span class="skill-icon">
					<Icon icon="article" color="currentColor" size="1.5rem" />
				</span>
				<h3>Developer onboarding</h3>
			</div>
			<p>
				Help developers reach first success faster with clear quickstarts and task-based guides.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="skill-card">
			<div class="skill-header">
				<span class="skill-icon">
					<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="currentColor" size="1.5rem" />
				</span>
				<h3>API documentation</h3>
			</div>
			<p>
				Design and structure API reference using OpenAPI and AsyncAPI, with examples, auth flows,
				and error handling.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="skill-card">
			<div class="skill-header">
				<span class="skill-icon">
					<Icon icon="sidebar" color="currentColor" size="1.5rem" />
				</span>
				<h3>Documentation architecture</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Organize content for clarity: navigation, hierarchy, and consistency across docs.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
